{"tid":2111100,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"有人與街上除罩食煙朋友吹水後雙雙確診","createTime":"2020-07-16T10:13:46.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-16T10:16:25.000Z","uid":255313,"like":8,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"a40020562693ad9755e3c1906c1e9d87cdcd6586","tid":2111100,"uid":255313,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-16T10:13:46.000Z","msg":"廢老唔戴罩 好似都冇除罩火車頭咁得人驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n在本地個案中，多宗涉及與友人聚會傳染。張竹君指出，第1649宗患者早前在街上遇到友人(第1456宗)，當時對方無戴口罩食煙，兩人站在街上10多分鐘，事後一同確診。另外， 第1647宗患者於7月11日曾與確診友人(第1473宗)及其餘數名友人聚餐，被安排入院檢測後確診。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nsource: tg, 蘋果"},{"pid":"2099a46fa0e5f6fa70bba906f4ce5245e943b46d","tid":2111100,"uid":269753,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-16T10:15:35.000Z","msg":"抵撚死<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/abomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e99c13e718a027d0ec0cc106a6835be3ae0163d1","tid":2111100,"uid":38904,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-16T10:15:55.000Z","msg":"煙剷點駁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"79655c4fc6d46e5bcb39f7075163a15ec1caf662","tid":2111100,"uid":224561,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-16T10:16:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lightbulb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lightbulb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}